"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-olympics-news-naomi-osaka-french-open-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The big news in Naomi Osaka's life has nothing to do with the French Open or clay-court tennis: Her 10-month-old daughter, Shai, is taking her first steps.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 155, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 16, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naomi_Osaka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Naomi Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naomi_Osaka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naomi_Osaka\"}, {\"begin\": 123, \"end\": 127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 3.355551145515815e-11, \"text\": \"Shai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yesterday, she walked for the first time, so I was really happy about that,\\\" Osaka said at Roland Garros on Saturday.\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are going to practice some more when I get back.\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it's really cool to have her here, just to see how much she's grown and how many things she's doing differently.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's kind of surreal.\\\"\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 468, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Sunday, Osaka outlasted 67th-ranked Italian Lucia Bronzetti 6-1, 4-6, 7-5 for her first French Open match win since 2021.\", \"from\": 470, \"to\": 594, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 481, \"end\": 486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9655497104356129, \"rank\": 0.034384881949097904, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were moments I played pretty well, but I was pretty nervous and got really tight,\\\" said the No.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 698, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"134-ranked Osaka of her hard-fought victory during an on-court interview.\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"FRENCH OPEN DRAWS:Men|Women|Broadcast Schedule  Up next could be what amounts to the toughest task these days in women's tennis: taking on No.\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 916, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"1 Iga Swiatek in the second round, should Swiatek win her first-round match Monday.\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 1000, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Swiatek is eyeing a third consecutive trophy at Roland Garros.\", \"from\": 1001, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Osaka is not quite there on clay herself, but she does say she is much more at ease these days.\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1065, \"end\": 1070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As any parent knows, being distant from kids while on the road for work is not easy.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1246, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Especially when the child is as little as Shai is - she will turn 1 in July.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1323, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1289, \"end\": 1293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\", \"score\": 0.9999999999663487, \"rank\": 3.355551145515815e-11, \"text\": \"Shai\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ga-Adangbe_people\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I mean, being away from her was really tough, but I called her every day,\\\" said Osaka, a former No.\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1406, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1-ranked player and four-time Grand Slam champion.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1476, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I saw how well she was doing and I saw how happy she was, so that made me happy, too.\\\"\", \"from\": 1477, \"to\": 1564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The European clay circuit began more than a month ago for Osaka in Rouen, France, then took her to Madrid and Rome.\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1624, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 1633, \"end\": 1638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\", \"score\": 0.9990752300872309, \"rank\": 0.0008943629034993021, \"text\": \"Rouen\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\"}, {\"begin\": 1640, \"end\": 1646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.6943753230389518, \"rank\": 0.4391351574902937, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1665, \"end\": 1671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Mutua_Madrid_Open\", \"score\": 0.969568315619569, \"rank\": 0.03138683875085238, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Mutua_Madrid_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Mutua_Madrid_Open\"}, {\"begin\": 1676, \"end\": 1680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"score\": 0.9986767900358687, \"rank\": 0.0013158299113090052, \"text\": \"Rome\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rome\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She lost her opener in Rouen, and her second match in Madrid.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1705, \"end\": 1710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\", \"score\": 0.9990752300872309, \"rank\": 0.0008943629034993021, \"text\": \"Rouen\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rouen\"}, {\"begin\": 1736, \"end\": 1742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Mutua_Madrid_Open\", \"score\": 0.969568315619569, \"rank\": 0.03138683875085238, \"text\": \"Madrid\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Mutua_Madrid_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2014_Mutua_Madrid_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was at the Italian Open that Osaka showed signs of having made serious strides on the slow, red surface that is not necessarily kind to her powerful strokes because it slows balls down.\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She had never won a match on clay against a player ranked in the top 20 until doing so twice there, getting past Marta Kostyuk and Daria Kasatkina along the way to reaching the fourth round.\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 2128, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2051, \"end\": 2064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marta_Kostyuk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Marta Kostyuk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marta_Kostyuk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Marta_Kostyuk\"}, {\"begin\": 2069, \"end\": 2074, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.007838106871242e-14, \"text\": \"Daria\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have made a significant amount of progress, and I feel like people can kind of see that throughout the tournaments that I have played,\\\" Osaka said.\", \"from\": 2130, \"to\": 2280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2269, \"end\": 2274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel like I have dedicated a lot of time to learning about clay.\\\"\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2349, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her major titles came in 2018-21 and all on hard courts, two apiece at the U.S. Open and Australian Open.\", \"from\": 2351, \"to\": 2456, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has yet to make it past the third round in Paris or on grass at Wimbledon.\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2504, \"end\": 2509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.807247915283213e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Repeated questions about difficulty on clay contributed to the anxiety and depression Osaka talked about experiencing when she declined to participate in news conferences at the 2021 French Open before withdrawing from the event.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2623, \"end\": 2628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"score\": 0.9996444498250353, \"rank\": 0.00035440158211867234, \"text\": \"Osaka\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\", \"Q13219666\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2011_HP_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was followed by a series of mental health breaks.\", \"from\": 2767, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She took more time away while she was pregnant, before returning to Grand Slam action at the Australian Open this January with a first-round loss.\", \"from\": 2823, \"to\": 2969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Honestly, at this point, I feel pretty comfortable on clay, to the point where I do not know if I will be a little confused my first day back on hard,\\\" she joked.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3134, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clay is fun.\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3149, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You get to slide around.\", \"from\": 3150, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You get to see how strong you are, in and out of corners,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For me, there is a lot of really valuable lessons that I am learning from clay-court tennis.\\\"\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3338, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Also Sunday, No.\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3 seed Carlos Alcaraz swept 107th-ranked American J.J. Wolf 6-1, 6-2, 6-1 in the Spaniard's first match since May 1.\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3364, \"end\": 3378, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Carlos Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Alcaraz\"}, {\"begin\": 3398, \"end\": 3406, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"score\": 0.9704173160106928, \"rank\": 0.020625307012150436, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6631808\", \"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_League\"}, {\"begin\": 3438, \"end\": 3446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.6367942329205646, \"rank\": 0.5703085302161451, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Alcaraz had been sidelined by a right forearm injury.\", \"from\": 3474, \"to\": 3527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3474, \"end\": 3481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.229930498901466e-20, \"text\": \"Alcaraz\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alcaraz\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am almost at 100% of my abilities,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3576, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After the match, I did not feel anything.\\\"\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3620, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a matchup of three-time major champions, Stan Wawrinka swept Andy Murray 6-4, 6-4, 6-2 in the night match.\", \"from\": 3622, \"to\": 3731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3666, \"end\": 3679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_Wawrinka\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stan Wawrinka\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_Wawrinka\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stan_Wawrinka\"}, {\"begin\": 3686, \"end\": 3697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.932615678092474e-70, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Physically tennis is not easy for me nowadays,\\\" said the 37-year-old Murray, who plans to play the doubles event with Dan Evans.\", \"from\": 3733, \"to\": 3862, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3803, \"end\": 3809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.2595151238540854e-49, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 3852, \"end\": 3861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"score\": 0.9753287969877489, \"rank\": 0.025295267696821604, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's hard, and clay has always been a surface that since the very beginning of my career I have had back issues on the clay, and it's something I am sort of used to, to be honest.\", \"from\": 3863, \"to\": 4043, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yeah, it had been a bit of a struggle in the training and in the buildup, but I felt pretty good going into the match tonight, considering.\", \"from\": 4044, \"to\": 4183, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It wasn't much of a factor out there this evening, to be honest.\\\"\", \"from\": 4184, \"to\": 4249, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The French Open continues Monday, live on NBC, NBCSports.com, the NBC Sports app andPeacockat 11 a.m.\", \"from\": 4251, \"to\": 4352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4298, \"end\": 4311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCSports.com\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 4317, \"end\": 4327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999804087856389, \"rank\": 1.9183669730653936e-05, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ET.\", \"from\": 4353, \"to\": 4356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A Division ofNBCUniversal.\", \"from\": 4360, \"to\": 4386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4360, \"end\": 4370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999408701132, \"rank\": 5.91300126274305e-08, \"text\": \"A Division\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Football_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DISCLAIMER: This site and the products offered are for entertainment purposes only, and there is no gambling offered on this site.\", \"from\": 4388, \"to\": 4518, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This service is intended for adult audiences.\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No guarantees are made for any specific outcome.\", \"from\": 4565, \"to\": 4613, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you or someone you know has a gambling problem, please call 1-800-GAMBLER.\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u24b8 2024 NBC Universal\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4713, \"entities\": []}]}"